com.tversity.sdk.android
Class AirFlinger

java.lang.Object
  com.tversity.sdk.android.AirFlinger

public abstract class AirFlinger
extends java.lang.Object

This class is the entry point to the AirFlinger SDK.

It contains one static method for retrieving the IAirFlinger interface and it defines all constants, callback interfaces, enums and exceptions used in the SDK
